    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXVIII. Nodalla.\nTahm divi Walstibahm Israël un Juh da tohv\nbeedinabts/ ka teem buhs pohstå eet / winno\nLepnibas / Plihteschanas/ un zittu negantu\nLeetu pehz to Lauschu : 1. Mahza no Kri-\nstus to dahrgu Stuhru-Akmini : 16. Jr/\nkapeh; Deews tehß Sawajus mehds pahr,\nmahziht : 23.\n1. Aj tam lepnam Kroh-\nnim ! teem Peedsehru-\nEcheem no Eewrâima /\nka Gohda Glihtums irr weena\ntawihtusi Puḱke / kas augscham\nus to tanhu Geletjn stahw/ teem/\nkas no Wihna irr pahrwarreti."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "2. Rangi/ weens stiprajs un\nwarrenajs no ta KUNGA/ itt\nka Kruffas Auḱt / ka fattigas\nWehtras/ itt ka warrenu Uhde-\nnu Pluhdi / kas warren us-\npluhst/ ta uomettihs wiꞥſch to\npee Semmes ar Warru."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "3. Tas lepnis Krohnis to\nPeedsehrufcho no Eewrâima taps\nar Kahjahin famihts."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Un ta wihtusi Puḱke win-\nna Gohda Glihtuma/ kas aug-\nscham us to tanhu Geleiju stahw/\nka weens agri eenabzis Auglis\npirns Waffaras Laika/ *kas no\nta/ kas to reds/un faivá Rohká\ndubbu tuhdalix tohp apehsta."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "* Jeb ta : Kas tohp apehsta, kad tas web\ntohp redsehts pee Sarra karrajain.\n5. Tai Deená buhs tas\nKUNGS Zebaot par weenu\nsaistu Krohni / un par weenu\nekabfchnu Wainagir teem Atlie-\nkutcheim fawo Lanschu."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Un par weenu Garru tuhs\nTeefafchanas tam/ las Teefas\nAmattá tehſch/ un par Stipru-\nmu teem/ kas to * Karzu no-\nwehrsch lihds Wahrtim."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "7. Schee arridsan irr no Wih-\nna pahrwarreti/ un straipale no\nstipra Dsehreena. Tas Prece-\nsteris un tas Praweets trakfo no\nstipra Dsehreena/ tee irr no Wih-\nna aprihti/ tee straipale no stipra\nDsehreena/ tee trakfo eeksch Pa-\nrahdischanahm/ un isweinij tahß\nTeefas."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Jo wiſſi Galdi ire pilli\nWemschanas un Neschfihstibas/\nka Weetas newaid."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Kurram tad warretu wiꞥſch\nto Atsishfchann mahziht? Un kur-\nram warretu wiꞥſch to Mahzibu\nsinnamu darriht ? teem Atschkir-\ntecun no Beena/ teem Noſchkir-\ntecun no Kruhtim."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Jo (tee jatta : ) pawehlt\npawehledams/ pawehlt pawehle-\ndams/ gaidi gaididams / gaidi\ngaididams / scheit maƙkeniht /\ntur maƙkeniht."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Tapehz wiꞥſch ar mehdt-\ndainahm Luhpahm/ un ar zittu\nMehli us scheem Landin run-\nnahs/us ko wiꞥſch ta ir runnajs."
    },
